---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

const title = "Privacy Policy";
const description = "SnapFitLabs Privacy Policy";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <section class="min-h-[calc(60vh)] flex flex-col">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="mb-6">
      At SnapFitLabs, we are committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy
      Policy outlines how we handle your data and your rights regarding your
      personal information.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">1. Data Collection</h2>
    <p class="mb-6">
      We do not collect any personal data from our users. Our app does not
      require you to provide any personal information, and we do not track your
      usage or behavior.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">2. Third-Party Data Sharing</h2>
    <p class="mb-6">
      Since we do not collect any personal data, we do not share any data with
      third parties. We do not use any analytics tools, advertising networks, or
      third-party SDKs that would require data sharing.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">3. Data Retention and Deletion</h2>
    <p class="mb-6">
      As we do not collect any personal data, there is no data to retain or
      delete. Your privacy is ensured by our policy of not collecting any data
      in the first place.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">
      4. User Consent and Data Deletion Requests
    </h2>
    <p class="mb-6">
      Since we do not collect any personal data, there is no need for you to
      revoke consent or request data deletion. Your privacy is protected by our
      commitment to not collecting any data.
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>
